Task uses the UHRS browser extension - link for download in the interface.
This task uses external web site for labeling.
Regular payment per page is $0.013.
To access paid work, training and qualification test should be passed.

In this task, you will see two product listings. The PRODUCT is a product that a user has bookmarked for 
which we would like to show them. The RECOMMENDED PRODUCT offers a product we 
might suggest to the user. The goal of this task is to classify these recommendations into one of the 
following categories based on how closely the RECOMMENDED PRODUCT matches the PRODUCT.

title: Check the similarity between two products
description:
In this task, you will see two product listings. The PRODUCT is a product that a user has bookmarked for 
which we would like to show them. The RECOMMENDED PRODUCT offers a product we 
might suggest to the user. The goal of this task is to classify these recommendations into one of the 
following categories based on how closely the RECOMMENDED PRODUCT matches the PRODUCT.
